title: Yoshimatsu
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Japanese, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Billed as healthy Japanese eatery, this casual place is attached to a full-service dining restaurant. Offers an extensive, separate vegetarian menu with several vegan choices. Order at the counter, and your server brings you the food. Very authentic Japanese decor. Also sells some Japanese gifts and things.
